stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Idle
  Idle --> LoadingGenerationRun: anchor_changed
  LoadingGenerationRun --> Ready: generation_run_loaded
  LoadingGenerationRun --> Ready: generation_run_missing / keep current
  Ready --> Planning: click/select/mode/question
  Planning --> Retrieving: plan_valid
  Planning --> Fallback: plan_timeout/error
  Retrieving --> Generating: context_ready
  Retrieving --> Unavailable: insufficient_context
  Generating --> Validating: candidates_ready
  Validating --> Repairing: repair_needed
  Repairing --> Validating: repaired_once
  Validating --> Streaming: pass
  Validating --> Unavailable: unrecoverable
  Streaming --> Committed: slot/scene commits
  Streaming --> Cancelled: newer uiVersion
  Committed --> Ready
  Fallback --> Ready
  Unavailable --> Ready
  Cancelled --> Ready
